  "texts": [
    "Neural Architecture Optimized FPN COCO 2017 Various Ghiasi et al., 2019",
    "In 2014, Girshick et al. (2014b) introduced a seminal approach to object detection by incorporating CNNs to enhance detection accuracy and improve bounding box quality through deep feature extraction.",
    "This method achieved a significant milestone, attaining a mean Average Precision (mAP) of 53.4%, a remarkable improvement over contemporaneous models.",
    "The model was trained on the PASCAL VOC 2012 benchmark dataset, setting a new standard for object detection tasks.",
    "A simplified representation of the RCNN process is illustrated in Figure 10."
  ]
}